ber 2023 demonstrated his power by removing his prime minister before dissolving parliament.\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 1186, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ivory Coast\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1000}, {\"ngram\": \"the economy\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1024}, {\"ngram\": \"Ouattara\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1049}, {\"ngram\": \"another strongman\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1082}, {\"ngram\": \"October\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"his power\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1125}, {\"ngram\": \"his prime minister\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1156}, {\"ngram\": \"parliament\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1185}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The decision was largely unchallenged.\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1228, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The decision\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1202}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Across Ivory Coast, there is very little criticism of the leader who marched the country out of one of its darkest episodes, not least in Abobo where the scars of war are evident by bullet holes in some of the crumbling tenement blocks.\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1465, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1367, \"end\": 1372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abobo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.981462136679889e-64, \"text\": \"Abobo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abobo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abobo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ivory Coast\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1247}, {\"ngram\": \"very little criticism\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1279}, {\"ngram\": \"the leader\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1293}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1317}, {\"ngram\": \"its darkest episodes\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1352}, {\"ngram\": \"the scars\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1388}, {\"ngram\": \"war\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1395}, {\"ngram\": \"bullet holes\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1423}, {\"ngram\": \"the crumbling tenement blocks\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1464}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe there should be no surprise that Ouattara gained much of his support here.\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1547, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no surprise\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1500}, {\"ngram\": \"Ouattara\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1514}, {\"ngram\": \"his support\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1541}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In simple terms, Abobo was one of the poorest parts of Abidjan and people felt like they were being ignored by the Gbagbo government.\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1681, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1565, \"end\": 1570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abobo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.981462136679889e-64, \"text\": \"Abobo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abobo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abobo\"}, {\"begin\": 1603, \"end\": 1610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abidjan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.9165648340502535e-76, \"text\": \"Abidjan\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abidjan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abidjan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"simple terms\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1563}, {\"ngram\": \"the poorest parts\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1599}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1621}, {\"ngram\": \"the Gbagbo government\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1680}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They wanted change but has that arrived?\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1722, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"change\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1700}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nobody seems to be willing to really say.\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1764, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nobody\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1729}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Politics remains a hushed subject in Ivory Coast, yet according to Amza Gamal, a certain fact remains.\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1867, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Politics\", \"